Package: locur
Type: Package
Title: Lorenz curves with ggplot2 and some common inequality measures.
Version: 1.0
Author: Jakob Bossek <jakob.bossek@tu-dortmund.de>
Maintainer: Jakob Bossek <jakob.bossek@tu-dortmund.de>
Encoding: UTF-8
Description: Draw neat Lorenz curves with the popular ggplot2 package and
    compute different inequality measures such as the Gini coefficient.
